  "id": "6423d85f230dbd001ceacaea",
  "title": "現代日本語が古語になる",
  "created": 1680070757,
  "updated": 1680071532,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6423d85f230dbd001ceacaea",
      "text": "現代日本語が古語になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680070757,
      "updated": 1680070773
    },
    {
      "id": "6423d86aaff09e00009dd52d",
      "text": "[現代日本語]が[古語]になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680070763,
      "updated": 1680070778
    },
    {
      "id": "6423d87aaff09e00009dd52f",
      "text": "　[英語公用語化論]の続き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680070779,
      "updated": 1680071347
    },
    {
      "id": "6423d885aff09e00009dd530",
      "text": "　公用語化するかしないか論争してる間に、市民の使う言葉が変化していき「2023年時点の日本語」が古語になる論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680070790,
      "updated": 1680070855
    },
    {
      "id": "6423d9cbaff09e00009dd532",
      "text": "　1872年: [学制令]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680071116,
      "updated": 1680071512
    },
    {
      "id": "6423dac8aff09e0000a30f99",
      "text": "\t1900年: 帝国教育会国語改良部「同音ノ仮名ニ数種アルヲ各一様ニ限ルコト（即チ[変体仮名]ヲ廃スルコト）」を議決",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680071370,
      "updated": 1680071524
    },
    {
      "id": "6423daefaff09e0000a30f9d",
      "text": "\t\t1908年異体字が一時的に復活したが、1922年にすべて廃止された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680071410,
      "updated": 1680071455
    },
    {
      "id": "6423db21aff09e0000a30f9e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/変体仮名 変体仮名 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680071460,
      "updated": 1680071485
    },
    {
      "id": "6423db45aff09e0000a30fa1",
      "text": "　1946年: [当用漢字]の制定",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680071496,
      "updated": 1680071531
    },
    {
      "id": "6423d8c8aff09e00009dd531",
      "text": "\t　「舊字體」を「旧字体」と書くようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1680070856,
      "updated": 1680071497
    },
